name: Chitty babu
description: As the Celo India Lead, a Celo Ambassador, and a participant in Celo Camp and have deep commitment to building the Celo ecosystem in India. active leader in community development through organizing training sessions and meetups, while also representing Celo at conferences and hackathons across the country. Notably, won the prestigious Celo Devpost Hackathon and a key contributor to the Celo platform.
